      "raw_text": "WASHINGTON, April 29.-Sec-\nrotary Ballinger has designated\n157176,8O0 acres of land in various\nstates to which the 800 acre home\nstead law applies as coming with\nIn provisions of the law. The\nstates are Oregon, Washington,\nUtah, Wyoming, New Mexico Ne\nvada, Arizona, Colorado, Montana.\n\n\nDiagrams showing lands subject\nto entry are being sent to local\nland offices. 1t is believed 40 per\ncent of the area designated, except\nIn Nevada, is held by individuals.\nIf all land were suitable there\nwould be $4,000 homessteads."
    }
